title: Battle for the ACC
description:
Wendi Nix, Tom Luginbill, and Rod Gilmore discuss this Saturday's Clemson v Miami match-up, the effects the Hurricane Delta is causing, the University of Houston finally getting to play their first game, and Zach Wilson of BYU.
